  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd-",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Singapore extends Gotabaya Rajapaksa's visa",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Sri Lankan President Gotabaya will continue to stay in Singapore as his visa has been extended, the country's Straits Times reported.",
        "The Straits Times reported that Singapore has further extended the short-term permit granted to Gotabaya Rajapaksa when he visited Singapore on the 14th.",
        "This information has come out as Cabinet Speaker Bandula Gunawardena said on Tuesday that Gotabaya Rajapaksa is coming back to Sri Lanka.",
        "The cabinet spokesperson said that it was not known when the former president would return to the country but he was not absconding.",
        "On the 14th, he was issued 14 visa when he arrived in Gothapaya from Maldives to Changi Airport by Saudia flight.",
        "He fled the country amid a deepening economic crisis and widespread protests against his government as rising inflation drove up the prices of essential commodities, including food and fuel.",
        "After arriving in Singapore, he announced his resignation, which was officially announced to the Sri Lankan Parliament on the 15th.",
        "His colleague Prime Minister Ranilwickramasinghe was elected as the new President by members of Parliament.",
        "It is known that the new visa granted to Gotabaya Rajapaksa will expire on the 11th.",
        "It is known that Rajapaksa initially stayed in a hotel in the city center and is currently staying in a private house.",
        "When he arrived in Singapore on the 14th, an official of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Singapore made a personal visit to him."
      ],
